How to Train Your Dragon;;91;;99;;PG;;Hiccup (Jay Baruchel) is a Norse teenager from the island of Berk, where fighting dragons is a way of life. His progressive views and weird sense of humor make him a misfit, despite the fact that his father (Gerard Butler) is chief of the clan. Tossed into dragon-fighting school, he endeavors to prove himself as a true Viking, but when he befriends an injured dragon he names Toothless, he has the chance to plot a new course for his people's future.;;Fantasy,Kids & family,Animation,Adventure,Comedy;;Christopher Sanders,Dean DeBlois;;2010;;Jay Baruchel,Gerard Butler,America Ferrera,Jonah Hill,Christopher Mintz-Plasse,Craig Ferguson,Kristen Wiig,T.J. Miller;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_to_train_your_dragon